<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>S. Baring-Gould</author>
<hymn_number>784</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jeso, be fitia !
 Zaza izahay,
 Avy mitaraina ;
 Mihainoa anay.

[V2]
 Bodo sy adala,
 Indreo ny zanakao ;
 Jeso ô, malala !
 Aza lavinao.

[V3]
 Mpiandry ondry mora !
 Mba tarihonao ;
 Tano tsy hania
 Ny ondrikelinao.

[V4]
 Aza avela hitady
 Laza aman-jo !
 Fa Hianao irery
 No mahafa-po.

[V5]
 Tianao ny zaza,
 Jeso ! fantatray
 Ka manolo-tena
 Ho Anao izahay.

[V6]
 Jeso be fitia !
 Zaza izahay,
 Avy mba hidera :
 Mihainoa anay.</lyrics>
<title>Jeso be fitia! FFPM784</title>
</song>